channel.title: Helping on testscape servers
channel.description:
i can code on testscape servers, but i want a few things
- good uptime, and owner knows what hes doing (compiling, and running server)
- he has msn, is nice and as soon as i did the first update i will get player rights 2 (or 3)
- he can NOT! buy/sell accounts, or mod/admin spots in his server, as i think its dumb
thats it.. you can speak to me trough msn bart_sloot@hotmail.com or just pm me
thank you for your time
P.S. for people who say i want to steal source aslong as you have the requirements ill even do an unedited source
the reason why i do this is: i see only pimp servers lately, wich i like but i want non-pk servers aswell
[br][size=1]Posted on: February 06, 2007, 07:37:54 AM[/size][hr]plz note i have experience
